&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;104241&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of the Eagle is an almost equally good alternative&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
